headline: Block to Announce Second Quarter 2025 Results
summary: DISTRIBUTED-WORK-MODEL/OAKLAND, Calif., July 10, 2025--Block, Inc. (NYSE: XYZ) will release financial results for the second quarter of 2025 on Thursday, August 7, 2025, after market close. Block will also host a conference call and earnings webcast at 2:00 p.m. Pacific Time/5:00 p.m. Eastern Time on the same day to discuss these results.

headline: Will Affirm Be a Long-Term Winner in a Crowded Fintech Space?
summary: AFRM shifts from big-ticket buys to daily spending as it scales transactions and deepens fintech competition footing.
